1
00:00:08,580 --> 00:00:09,700
<i>Hi.</i>
<i>你好</i>

2
00:00:10,940 --> 00:00:12,980
<i>I'm looking for a seed.</i>
<i>我在找一顆種子</i>

3
00:00:13,620 --> 00:00:15,820
<i>Red, small.</i>
<i>紅色，小小的</i>

4
00:00:19,820 --> 00:00:21,940
<i>A little seed, this big.</i>
<i>小小一顆，大概這麼大</i>

5
00:00:22,060 --> 00:00:24,580
<i>Grows into a round plant,</i>
<i>長在環繞的植物上</i>

6
00:00:24,700 --> 00:00:26,460
<i>this high...</i>
<i>這麼高...</i>

7
00:00:26,620 --> 00:00:28,020
<i>Does it flower?</i>
<i>它會開花嗎？</i>

8
00:00:28,100 --> 00:00:30,820
<i>No, you can't eat it.</i>
<i>不行，你不能吃它</i>

9
00:00:31,060 --> 00:00:33,220
<i>The plant is about this high.</i>
<i>那個植物會長這麼高</i>

10
00:00:34,860 --> 00:00:36,540
<i>Is it sold here?</i>
<i>在這裡有賣嗎？</i>

11
00:00:37,860 --> 00:00:40,500
<i>I was told I could buy it here.</i>
<i>我聽說這裡可以買到</i>

12
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:44,540
<i>Where can I buy it?</i>
<i>哪裡可以買呢？</i>

13
00:00:45,900 --> 00:00:48,500
<i>Where can I buy it?</i>
<i>哪裡可以買呢？</i>

14
00:00:49,180 --> 00:00:51,858
<i>It's too late.</i>
<i>太遲了</i>

15
00:00:51,958 --> 00:00:54,724
<i>Ok, thanks.</i>
<i>好吧，謝謝</i>

16
00:01:05,060 --> 00:01:06,980
<i>Hi, I'm looking for a little red seed.</i>
<i>你好，我在找一顆紅色的小種子</i>

17
00:01:07,420 --> 00:01:09,100
<i>A little seed.</i>
<i>一顆小種子</i>

18
00:01:09,660 --> 00:01:11,220
<i>I don't know its name.</i>
<i>我不知道它的名字</i>

19
00:01:11,820 --> 00:01:12,900
<i>What?</i>
<i>什麼？</i>

20
00:01:13,380 --> 00:01:14,460
<i>What?</i>
<i>什麼？</i>

21
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,940
<i>No, that's not it. A seed.</i>
<i>不是，不是這個，是種子</i>

22
00:01:20,700 --> 00:01:22,780
<i>That I'm falling?</i>
<i>我在往下掉？</i>

23
00:01:22,860 --> 00:01:24,203
<i>That's why he's so fat.</i>
<i>這就是為什麼他這麼胖</i>

24
00:01:24,253 --> 00:01:25,450
<i>During the day he barely eats.</i>
<i>他在白天幾乎不吃東西</i>

25
00:01:25,500 --> 00:01:27,340
<i>His body goes on high alert.</i>
<i>他身體其實也發出警訊了</i>

26
00:01:27,580 --> 00:01:29,100
<i>When he pigs out at night</i>
<i>他在半夜像豬一樣大吃時</i>

27
00:01:29,180 --> 00:01:32,460
<i>his body thinks it needs to absorb everything.</i>
<i>他的身體認為他需要全部都吸收</i>

28
00:01:37,620 --> 00:01:40,580
<i>So it's better to eat a little at a time.</i>
<i>所以少量多餐還是比較好</i>

29
00:01:41,780 --> 00:01:42,980
<i>Are you listening?</i>
<i>你有在聽嗎？</i>

30
00:01:43,340 --> 00:01:45,660
<i>Yes. All the way down?</i>
<i>有。一直往下走嗎？</i>

31
00:01:45,780 --> 00:01:46,780
<i>Yes.</i>
<i>對</i>

32
00:01:48,900 --> 00:01:50,260
<i>Know where it is?</i>
<i>你知道它在哪裡嗎？</i>

33
00:01:51,620 --> 00:01:52,660
<i>No.</i>
<i>不知道</i>

34
00:01:55,260 --> 00:01:56,500
<i>I'm hungry.</i>
<i>我好餓唷</i>

35
00:02:03,460 --> 00:02:04,460
Thanks.
謝謝

36
00:02:17,780 --> 00:02:21,020
<i>Why show my feelings if we never talk?</i>
<i>如果我們不交談，何必顯露我的情緒呢？</i>

37
00:02:25,020 --> 00:02:26,260
What're they doing?
他們在做什麼？

38
00:02:29,020 --> 00:02:30,780
<i>I think they're going out.</i>
<i>我想他們要出去了</i>

39
00:02:31,140 --> 00:02:32,420
<i>No, guys like you.</i>
<i>不是，是那些像你一樣的傢伙</i>

40
00:02:33,220 --> 00:02:34,580
<i>What do you mean?</i>
<i>你什麼意思阿？</i>

41
00:02:37,420 --> 00:02:39,780
I think I'll skip work tomorrow.
我想我明天會翹班

42
00:02:40,660 --> 00:02:42,420
You always say that.
你每天都這麼說

43
00:02:42,540 --> 00:02:44,300
Look, I cut my finger.
看！我切到手指了

44
00:02:44,420 --> 00:02:45,900
That's normal.
這很正常阿

45
00:02:46,020 --> 00:02:47,900
Normal for you, not for me.
對你來說很正常，對我不是

46
00:02:47,980 --> 00:02:49,300
You drinking a beer?
你喝啤酒嗎？

47
00:02:50,300 --> 00:02:52,540
Are you kidding? Obviously.
你在開玩笑嗎？ 當然阿！

48
00:02:52,620 --> 00:02:54,980
I can't see, but I can smell it.
我看不出，但我聞的出

49
00:02:59,220 --> 00:03:00,300
You can't see?
你看不到？

50
00:03:02,660 --> 00:03:04,780
<i>My eyes need to adjust.</i>
<i>我的眼睛需要一些調整</i>

51
00:03:05,300 --> 00:03:07,660
<i>Let's play "Say it, win it!"</i>
<i>我們來玩[敢說就贏了]</i>

52
00:03:15,420 --> 00:03:16,660
You lie.
你說謊

53
00:03:17,020 --> 00:03:18,020
What?
什麼？

54
00:03:19,540 --> 00:03:21,060
<i>He's a big liar.</i>
<i>他是個大騙子</i>

55
00:03:21,380 --> 00:03:23,420
It's no fun playing with you.
跟你玩一點都不好玩

56
00:03:24,180 --> 00:03:25,759
<i>My shoes!</i>
<i>我的鞋子！</i>

57
00:03:25,859 --> 00:03:28,049
<i>Take them off.</i>
<i>把它們脫了</i>

58
00:03:27,140 --> 00:03:29,740
<i>Let's order pizza. It'll do us good.</i>
<i>我們來叫比薩吧，這對我們好</i>

59
00:03:31,020 --> 00:03:32,220
Go for it.
好阿叫吧

60
00:03:42,940 --> 00:03:43,980
Yep.
好耶

61
00:03:44,260 --> 00:03:45,260
Cool.
酷

62
00:03:56,540 --> 00:03:58,860
I dreamt air was like dough.
我夢見空氣就像麵團一樣

63
00:03:59,100 --> 00:04:00,100
What?
什麼？

64
00:04:00,180 --> 00:04:01,452
Bread dough.
做麵包的那種？

65
00:04:01,552 --> 00:04:02,059
Raw?
生麵團？

66
00:04:03,820 --> 00:04:06,700
And I destroyed myself to understand.
我為了搞懂這一切差點毀了自己

67
00:04:09,900 --> 00:04:10,860
What are you doing?
你在做什麼？

68
00:04:11,180 --> 00:04:12,460
Nothing.
沒有阿

69
00:04:12,740 --> 00:04:13,940
Say it, win it.
說出來，你就贏了

70
00:04:14,580 --> 00:04:17,779
I thought you were making fun of me.
我以為你在開我玩笑

71
00:04:25,860 --> 00:04:28,540
<i>Why show my feelings if we never talk?</i>
<i>如果我們不交談，何必顯露我的情緒呢？</i>

72
00:04:46,700 --> 00:04:48,140
I don't want to go.
我不想走

73
00:04:48,500 --> 00:04:50,140
So what's your hurry?
那你在趕什麼？

74
00:04:50,460 --> 00:04:52,340
No other openings.
沒有別家是開的

75
00:04:52,940 --> 00:04:53,980
Oh well.
是阿

76
00:04:54,220 --> 00:04:55,420
She's a bitch.
她真是個賤人

77
00:04:56,820 --> 00:04:58,180
My shoulder hurts.
我肩膀痛死了

78
00:04:59,140 --> 00:05:00,140
Look.
你看

79
00:05:00,380 --> 00:05:01,700
Did she do that?
是她弄的？

80
00:05:02,060 --> 00:05:03,340
Indirectly, yes.
間接的，算是

81
00:05:06,740 --> 00:05:08,300
Sure this is the way?
你確定是這條路？

82
00:05:12,620 --> 00:05:14,007
Vacation is no vacation
如果我一直做重複的事情，

83
00:05:14,107 --> 00:05:15,699
if I keep doing the same thing.
假日就稱不上假日了

84
00:05:18,820 --> 00:05:19,940
Are you listening?
你有在聽嗎？

85
00:05:24,580 --> 00:05:25,860
Got the flowers?
拿到花了沒？

86
00:05:26,700 --> 00:05:27,740
Yep.
嗯哼

87
00:05:28,140 --> 00:05:29,460
Where'd you put them?
你把它們放在哪裡了？

88
00:05:32,740 --> 00:05:33,900
Tell me.
快告訴我

89
00:05:35,780 --> 00:05:38,180
Deep inside in total safety.
在很安全的深處

90
00:05:41,900 --> 00:05:44,100
That way I'm sure they're safe.
這樣我才能確保它們是平安的

91
00:05:44,340 --> 00:05:46,140
Spare me the details.
細節就不用說了

92
00:05:47,820 --> 00:05:48,860
Want some?
要一些嗎？

93
00:05:50,260 --> 00:05:51,420
No, thanks.
不用了，謝謝

94
00:05:58,100 --> 00:05:58,464
What?
什麼？

95
00:05:58,564 --> 00:06:00,899
That you should put it in the bag.
那你應該把它放在背包裡阿

96
00:06:01,020 --> 00:06:03,980
Oh, I heard it, you said jungle.
我-聽-到-了，你說叢林

97
00:06:08,780 --> 00:06:10,380
So, are you coming tonight ?
那所以，你今晚會來嗎？

98
00:06:11,220 --> 00:06:13,980
I don't think so, I don't have any money.
我不覺得，我沒錢了

99
00:06:14,260 --> 00:06:16,380
Don't worry, I'll lend you some.
又沒差，我借你阿

100
00:06:16,460 --> 00:06:19,740
No, it's fine, if I don't have, I don't have.
不用啦，沒關係。如果我沒錢，就沒錢阿

101
00:06:23,020 --> 00:06:24,380
Hey, Archie !
嘿Archie！

102
00:06:28,700 --> 00:06:29,940
What's up?
你好嗎？

103
00:06:30,740 --> 00:06:32,180
I'm good.
還不錯啦

104
00:06:32,460 --> 00:06:33,629
Are you going this way?
你也往這邊嗎？

105
00:06:33,729 --> 00:06:34,819
Yes, I'm coming home.
嗯，我正要回家

106
00:06:35,660 --> 00:06:38,900
I forgot to tell I will stay out too late.
我忘記說我快遲到了

107
00:06:39,260 --> 00:06:41,177
So where you with Kinny last night?
所以你昨晚跟Kinny在一起？

108
00:06:41,277 --> 00:06:41,699
No ...
沒有...

109
00:06:42,380 --> 00:06:45,140
He texted me that they were doing a party downstairs.
阿，他傳簡訊說他在樓下開啪踢

110
00:06:45,660 --> 00:06:48,700
But I was already on my bed, eating cheese, drunk,
但我已經醉倒在我床上，還吃著起司

111
00:06:49,220 --> 00:06:50,540
so I didn't feel like going.
所以我超不想去的

112
00:06:50,660 --> 00:06:52,110
I turned off the phone, lights,
我關了手機，燈，

113
00:06:52,210 --> 00:06:53,660
everything. I dissapeared.
所有的東西，像我消失了一樣

114
00:06:54,180 --> 00:06:55,860
I think I'm getting old.
我覺得我在變老

115
00:06:56,580 --> 00:06:58,156
So you're not coming tonight?
所以你今晚真的不來唷？

116
00:06:58,256 --> 00:06:59,059
I don't think so.
應該不會

117
00:06:59,340 --> 00:07:02,980
I think he wants to spend time with Alf and Bobby.
我覺得他比較想跟Alf 和 Bobby相處

118
00:07:03,060 --> 00:07:04,540
Stop lying!
少在那邊亂講！

119
00:07:07,180 --> 00:07:10,100
I bought a new plant. It's funny.
我買了一個新植物，它很妙

120
00:07:11,020 --> 00:07:13,106
This tree is new too, right?
這些樹也是新的，對嘛？

121
00:07:13,206 --> 00:07:13,539
Yes.
沒錯

122
00:07:14,540 --> 00:07:16,020
And why is it funny?
那它妙在哪呢？

123
00:07:16,500 --> 00:07:19,220
You never know how it'll act with you.
你猜不到它會怎麼跟你互動的

124
00:07:21,300 --> 00:07:22,500
What's it called?
它叫什麼？

125
00:07:22,700 --> 00:07:24,140
Armadillo tail.
犰狳尾

126
00:07:25,460 --> 00:07:26,500
What's it do
它能做什麼？

127
00:07:26,780 --> 00:07:28,500
Makes me want to see pictures of girls.
讓我想看女孩子的照片

128
00:07:29,220 --> 00:07:30,396
Girls?
女孩子？

129
00:07:30,496 --> 00:07:31,059
Yep.
對

130
00:07:42,140 --> 00:07:43,420
Have you talked to Paul ?
你跟Paul講過話了嘛？

131
00:07:44,460 --> 00:07:44,962
No
沒耶

132
00:07:45,062 --> 00:07:45,979
Sorry
抱歉

133
00:07:46,740 --> 00:07:48,580
I've not been able to talk to Paul
我一直沒辦法跟Paul講話

134
00:07:48,700 --> 00:07:50,980
because I've got no light for some days now.
因為我已經有一陣子沒燈可用了

135
00:07:51,180 --> 00:07:52,500
Ah, so you're still without light
蛤！所以你一直沒有燈唷！

136
00:07:53,140 --> 00:07:54,464
Yeah, twenty days !
對阿，二十天了耶

137
00:07:54,564 --> 00:07:55,379
Twenty days ?
二十天！

138
00:07:58,300 --> 00:08:01,734
You can come to my house if you want.
你可以來我家阿，如果你想

139
00:08:01,834 --> 00:08:02,139
Ok.
好哇

140
00:08:03,260 --> 00:08:04,260
Mabel !

141
00:08:12,260 --> 00:08:13,111
What are you doing here?
你在這裡幹嘛？

142
00:08:13,211 --> 00:08:14,179
Hey! Where are you going?
哈囉！你要去哪裡？

143
00:08:14,380 --> 00:08:16,442
I'm going to school, you ?
我要去學校阿，你呢？

144
00:08:16,542 --> 00:08:17,900
I'm going to work.
我要去上班了

145
00:08:18,300 --> 00:08:19,702
Oh, that's nice.
喔，那不錯阿

146
00:08:19,802 --> 00:08:20,940
I don't know.
我不知道耶

147
00:08:21,620 --> 00:08:22,937
You don't know what ?
你不知道什麼？

148
00:08:23,037 --> 00:08:24,259
Going to work ...
要不要去上班阿...

149
00:08:24,860 --> 00:08:27,340
Ok, come this way.
好，那你走這條路

150
00:08:27,660 --> 00:08:29,020
Is it this way to your school ?
這是你去學校的路嗎？

151
00:08:29,140 --> 00:08:32,460
No. I come here when I don't want to go to school.
沒有，我不想去學校的時候我才走這條路。

152
00:08:39,020 --> 00:08:40,500
I want to learn music,
我想知道跟音樂有關的事情，

153
00:08:41,500 --> 00:08:42,940
and download music.
然後也下載一些新音樂

154
00:08:44,300 --> 00:08:45,318
You want?
你要嗎？

155
00:08:45,418 --> 00:08:45,779
No.
不用

156
00:08:46,340 --> 00:08:47,540
I'm ok.
我這樣就可以

157
00:09:00,780 --> 00:09:02,900
In what could I specialize?
我應該專攻什麼呢？

158
00:09:04,740 --> 00:09:06,620
Maybe you could work in a supermarket.
也許你可以在超級市場工作

159
00:09:06,740 --> 00:09:10,300
Yes ! I will learn more about music there.
沒錯！我在那裡可以學更多音樂的知識（才怪）

160
00:09:36,020 --> 00:09:37,900
In what could I specialize?
我該專攻什麼？

161
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:41,180
Are you listening ?
你有在聽嗎？

162
00:09:43,140 --> 00:09:45,140
Doctor, I think this guy is lying.
教授，我認為這個人在撒謊

163
00:09:46,580 --> 00:09:48,380
But it's not important.
但這並不重要

164
00:09:49,060 --> 00:09:50,060
Really?
真的嗎？

165
00:09:50,180 --> 00:09:52,260
Do we need to find a psychiatrist for him?
我們需要為他找一位心理醫生嗎？

166
00:09:52,540 --> 00:09:54,220
Not that much.
也沒那麼誇張

167
00:09:55,620 --> 00:09:57,220
Well, let's send him out.
叫他離開這裡

168
00:09:59,660 --> 00:10:00,660
Please !
拜託你！

169
00:10:01,140 --> 00:10:04,180
It's just a minute.
只要一分鐘就好！

170
00:10:04,900 --> 00:10:06,180
<i>I've got all the papers !</i>
<i>我所有的報告都寫好了</i>

171
00:10:07,380 --> 00:10:08,740
<i>I won't come again,</i>
<i>我不會再來了</i>

172
00:10:10,700 --> 00:10:12,500
<i>I swear.</i>
<i>我發誓</i>

173
00:10:29,020 --> 00:10:31,700
Was that already here? Is it new?
這本來就在這邊的嗎？這是新的嗎？

174
00:10:45,820 --> 00:10:47,300
I need more money.
我需要更多錢

175
00:10:47,420 --> 00:10:48,860
<i>Soon.</i>
<i>快了</i>

176
00:10:50,380 --> 00:10:52,380
I still don't believe in reincarnation.
我還是不相信投胎輪迴

177
00:10:58,220 --> 00:10:59,380
Ten more.
還有十個

178
00:11:01,620 --> 00:11:02,660
<i>Three...</i>
<i>三個...</i>

179
00:11:06,140 --> 00:11:07,940
<i>Well... five.</i>
<i>好吧，五個...</i>

180
00:11:25,100 --> 00:11:27,140
Sleeping in the daytime isn't sleep.
做白日夢不算是睡覺阿

181
00:11:29,780 --> 00:11:32,500
When I was little I said "dead" for "bed".
我小時候都把 "床" 說成 "亡"

182
00:11:48,020 --> 00:11:49,580
<i>Find the seeds?</i>
<i>找到種子了嗎？</i>

183
00:12:21,620 --> 00:12:24,700
<i>Another time you might fall in love with me.</i>
<i>下一次，也許你會愛上我</i>
